# Tell GitHub Linguist that the vendored harness is not our code.
# Effects:
#   - vendor/ contribution is excluded from the repo's language stats
#   - vendor/ is excluded from PR diff stats by default
#   - linguist-treated as "vendored", which collapses it in PR review UI
#
# This is correct and standard for any pinned third-party source we vendor
# verbatim. See vendor/archipelago/UPSTREAM.md for the pinned commit.
vendor/** linguist-vendored=true
